TO THE COOK FROM BRIDGEWATER, NJ: The riginal recipe calls for 1 1/2 cups of graham cracker crumbs. This particular recipe calls for you to use 3/4 cup of graham cracker crumbs and 3/4 cup of gingersnap crumbs. Hope this will help clarify the directions for you. TO PAT MAZUR: You are correct in thinking that a 10" springform pan would be the best to use.

